## 六、Max 形象应用规范

### 6.1 小头像（游戏界面）

```css
.max-face {
  width: 48px;
  height: 48px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  border: 3px solid #2196F3;
  background-image: url('assets/max_character.jpg');
  background-size: 200%;
  background-position: 50% 15%;  /* 裁剪头部区域 */
}
```

### 6.2 全身像（结算界面）

```css
.complete-mascot {
  width: 180px;
  height: 180px;
  background-image: url('assets/max_character.jpg');
  background-size: contain;
  background-position: center;
  animation: mascotBounce 1s ease infinite alternate;
}
```

### 6.3 动画效果

```css
@keyframes mascotBounce {
  0% { transform: translateY(0) rotate(-3deg); }
  100% { transform: translateY(-10px) rotate(3deg); }
}
```

